-- Alcatel-Lucent Plans to Sell Adixen Unit, Les Echos Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-07T04:08:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/alcatel-lucent-plans-to-sell-adixen-unit-les-echos-says.html
Alcatel-Lucent plans to sell its
Adixen pump-making unit, Les Echos reported, without saying how
it got the information.  The company hopes to raise 200 million euros through the
sale, the newspaper said. Alcatel executives are still debating
whether to sell Alcatel-Lucent Submarine Systems, the newspaper
added, citing an unidentified banker.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  